Title: 021: Applications of Data Science, Democratizing AI and Advice with Sinan Ozdemir
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Data Science Author Sinan Ozdemir. You will learn the different applications of data science, advance your knowledge in democratizing AI and hear advices that will help the learners of data science.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/21
